"use strict";(self.webpackChunkbibtex=self.webpackChunkbibtex||[]).push([[8751],{7927:function(e){e.exports=JSON.parse('{"blogPosts":[{"id":"how-to-format-citations-and-bibliographies-in-rstudio-with-citedrive-and-quarto","metadata":{"permalink":"/cs/blog/how-to-format-citations-and-bibliographies-in-rstudio-with-citedrive-and-quarto","editUrl":"https://github.com/citedrive/bibtex.eu/blog/blog/2022-08-28-quarto.md","source":"@site/i18n/cs/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2022-08-28-quarto.md","title":"How to Format Citations and Bibliographies in RStudio with CiteDrive and Quarto","description":"Tato str\xe1nka je v sou\u010dasn\xe9 dob\u011b k dispozici pouze v angli\u010dtin\u011b, ale velmi bychom pot\u0159ebovali va\u0161i pomoc s jej\xedm p\u0159ekladem do va\u0161eho jazyka! Pokud m\xe1te z\xe1jem, pod\xedvejte se na na\u0161e \xfalo\u017ei\u0161t\u011b GitHub, kde najdete dal\u0161\xed informace o tom, jak p\u0159isp\u011bt.","date":"2022-08-28T00:00:00.000Z","formattedDate":"28. srpna 2022","tags":[{"label":"citedrive","permalink":"/cs/blog/tags/citedrive"},{"label":"rstudio","permalink":"/cs/blog/tags/rstudio"},{"label":"quarto","permalink":"/cs/blog/tags/quarto"},{"label":"rmarkdown","permalink":"/cs/blog/tags/rmarkdown"}],"readingTime":2.755,"hasTruncateMarker":false,"authors":[{"name":"CiteDrive","title":"https://www.citedrive.com/","mail":"hello@citedrive.com","url":"https://www.citedrive.com/","image_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/65911387?s=200&v=4","imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/65911387?s=200&v=4"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"how-to-format-citations-and-bibliographies-in-rstudio-with-citedrive-and-quarto","title":"How to Format Citations and Bibliographies in RStudio with CiteDrive and Quarto","authors":{"name":"CiteDrive","title":"https://www.citedrive.com/","mail":"hello@citedrive.com","url":"https://www.citedrive.com/","image_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/65911387?s=200&v=4","imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/65911387?s=200&v=4"},"tags":["citedrive","rstudio","quarto","rmarkdown"]},"nextItem":{"title":"Citov\xe1n\xed a pou\u017e\xedv\xe1n\xed odkaz\u016f na Overleafu: P\u0159\xedru\u010dka pro v\xfdzkumn\xe9 pracovn\xedky","permalink":"/cs/blog/citing-and-using-references-on-overleaf-a-guide-for-researchers"}},"content":":::note\\nTato str\xe1nka je v sou\u010dasn\xe9 dob\u011b k dispozici pouze v angli\u010dtin\u011b, ale velmi bychom pot\u0159ebovali va\u0161i pomoc s jej\xedm p\u0159ekladem do va\u0161eho jazyka! Pokud m\xe1te z\xe1jem, pod\xedvejte se na na\u0161e \xfalo\u017ei\u0161t\u011b GitHub, kde najdete dal\u0161\xed informace o tom, jak p\u0159isp\u011bt.\\n:::\\n\\n\\n# How to Format Citations and Bibliographies in RStudio with CiteDrive and Quarto\\n\\n\\nDo you need to format citations and a bibliography for a research paper in RStudio? Are you struggling to keep track of all your references and formatting requirements? Have no fear! CiteDrive and Quarto can help. This blog post will show you how to use both tools to create beautiful, correctly formatted citations and bibliographies.\\n\\n\\n## Get started\\n\\nTo format citations and bibliographies in RStudio with CiteDrive and Quarto, follow these steps:\\n\\n\\n### Step 1: Include references in your project\\n\\nFirst, you must create a CiteDrive account by going to their website and selecting the \'Sign Up\' button. Completing your account will then enable you to make an \'R-Markdown\' (*it works for Quarto, don\'t you worry*) project; simply name it and [fill the project with references](https://citedrive.medium.com/adding-bibliographic-references-to-rstudio-using-citedrive-create-citations-in-r-markdown-or-9b1e1ab59cf6). Yours might look something like this:\\n\\n![CiteDrive - Example](@site/static/img/tutorial/citedrive_project_example.png)\\n\\n### Step 2:  Connect your Quarto document to CiteDrive\\n\\nNow, let\'s connect your new CiteDrive to your Quarto document. To do this, click the \'bib\' button. This will open up a new tab with all your entries in BibTeX format. Copy the URL from the new tab and paste it into the YAML part of your QMD file.\\n\\n\\n````md\\n---\\nbibliography: \\"https://api.citedrive.com/bib/514b115a-e8b7-4e14-a7c8-83e88337ad12/references.bib?x=eyJpZCI6ICI1MTRiFTE1YS1lOGI3LTRlMTQtYTdjOC04M2U4ODMzN2FkMTIiLCAidXNlciI6ICI5NzgiLCAic2lnbmF0dXJlIjogIjBkZDgzNGM1NDg2YzE2MTRhYTUzZDAyNmI1YjFhZjgxNTg3ODc4NDQ3Yzk1ODQ1ZWI2ZTA5UTQ5YTFlNDdlMGIifQ==.bib\\"\\n---\\n````\\n\\nThe following clip shows the flow when using R Markdown. However, the principle of Quarto is the same:\\n\\n<iframe width=\\"100%\\" height=\\"315\\" src=\\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/7ON96F0GD-Y\\" title=\\"YouTube video player\\" frameborder=\\"0\\" allow=\\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\\n\\n### Step 3: Copy the citation keys.\\n\\nOnce your references are imported, you can insert them into your Quarto document. To do this, return to your CiteDrive project and one or more references your want to insert into your document and click the cite button. CiteDrive will copy the citation key to your clipboard.\\n\\n![CiteDrive - Example](@site/static/img/tutorial/citedrive_copy_citation.gif)\\n\\nPaste your citation key in the necessary passage of your Quarto document.\\n\\n![CiteDrive - Paste citationkey](@site/static/img/tutorial/citedrive_paste_citation_rstudio.gif)\\n\\n\\nAfter you insert the key in the section, click \u201crender.\u201d The citation will be outputted in your desired style, and the reference will appear at the end of your document.\\n\\nThat\'s all! CiteDrive is the perfect tool to help you manage your bibliography and insert citations into Quarto documents. Test it out now and see how much time it can save you!\\n\\n## Additional information\\n\\n### Quarto\\nQuarto is a powerful research writing tool that can automatically generate citations and bibliographies in various styles. It supports bibliography files in BibTeX and other formats, making it easy to keep track of your references.\\n\\n\\n### CiteDrive\\nCiteDrive is a reference management tool that allows you to organize, store easily, and search your bibliographic data. Organize your teams and references in projects, for example, for a dedicated Quarto paper. CiteDrive automatically keeps your references in Quarto up-to-date whenever you or one of your teammates updates the bibliographic data within your project.\\n\\nDo you prefer BibLaTeX? No problem, CiteDrive is 100 % BibTeX empowered and provides freedom in fields and types for each entry, meaning you can use any BibTeX-based package or alternative, like BibLaTeX."},{"id":"citing-and-using-references-on-overleaf-a-guide-for-researchers","metadata":{"permalink":"/cs/blog/citing-and-using-references-on-overleaf-a-guide-for-researchers","editUrl":"https://github.com/citedrive/bibtex.eu/blog/blog/2022-08-16-doi-bibtex.md","source":"@site/i18n/cs/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2022-08-16-doi-bibtex.md","title":"Citov\xe1n\xed a pou\u017e\xedv\xe1n\xed odkaz\u016f na Overleafu: P\u0159\xedru\u010dka pro v\xfdzkumn\xe9 pracovn\xedky","description":"P\u0159i psan\xed v\xfdzkumn\xe9 pr\xe1ce je d\u016fle\u017eit\xe9 pou\u017e\xedvat odkazy na podporu sv\xfdch tvrzen\xed. Spr\xe1vn\xe9 citov\xe1n\xed zdroj\u016f je kl\xed\u010dem k vytvo\u0159en\xed solidn\xed argumentace a vyhnut\xed se plagi\xe1torstv\xed. Tento pr\u016fvodce v\xe1m uk\xe1\u017ee, jak citovat odkazy na Overleaf pomoc\xed CiteDrive. Poskytneme v\xe1m tak\xe9 tipy, jak naj\xedt spolehliv\xe9 zdroje online. Poj\u010fme za\u010d\xedt!","date":"2022-08-16T00:00:00.000Z","formattedDate":"16. srpna 2022","tags":[{"label":"citedrive","permalink":"/cs/blog/tags/citedrive"},{"label":"overleaf","permalink":"/cs/blog/tags/overleaf"},{"label":"latex","permalink":"/cs/blog/tags/latex"},{"label":"bibtex","permalink":"/cs/blog/tags/bibtex"},{"label":"biblatex","permalink":"/cs/blog/tags/biblatex"},{"label":"natbib","permalink":"/cs/blog/tags/natbib"}],"readingTime":3.58,"hasTruncateMarker":false,"authors":[{"name":"CiteDrive","title":"https://www.citedrive.com/","mail":"hello@citedrive.com","url":"https://www.citedrive.com/","image_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/65911387?s=200&v=4","imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/65911387?s=200&v=4"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"citing-and-using-references-on-overleaf-a-guide-for-researchers","title":"Citov\xe1n\xed a pou\u017e\xedv\xe1n\xed odkaz\u016f na Overleafu: P\u0159\xedru\u010dka pro v\xfdzkumn\xe9 pracovn\xedky","authors":{"name":"CiteDrive","title":"https://www.citedrive.com/","mail":"hello@citedrive.com","url":"https://www.citedrive.com/","image_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/65911387?s=200&v=4","imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/65911387?s=200&v=4"},"tags":["citedrive","overleaf","latex","bibtex","biblatex","natbib"]},"prevItem":{"title":"How to Format Citations and Bibliographies in RStudio with CiteDrive and Quarto","permalink":"/cs/blog/how-to-format-citations-and-bibliographies-in-rstudio-with-citedrive-and-quarto"},"nextItem":{"title":"Jak p\u0159ev\xe9st DOI na citaci v BibTeXu pomoc\xed CiteDrive","permalink":"/cs/blog/how-to-convert-a-doi-to-a-bibtex-citation-using-citedrive"}},"content":"P\u0159i psan\xed v\xfdzkumn\xe9 pr\xe1ce je d\u016fle\u017eit\xe9 pou\u017e\xedvat odkazy na podporu sv\xfdch tvrzen\xed. Spr\xe1vn\xe9 citov\xe1n\xed zdroj\u016f je kl\xed\u010dem k vytvo\u0159en\xed solidn\xed argumentace a vyhnut\xed se plagi\xe1torstv\xed. Tento pr\u016fvodce v\xe1m uk\xe1\u017ee, jak citovat odkazy na Overleaf pomoc\xed CiteDrive. Poskytneme v\xe1m tak\xe9 tipy, jak naj\xedt spolehliv\xe9 zdroje online. Poj\u010fme za\u010d\xedt!\\n\\n\\n\\n## Krok 1: Propojen\xed aplikace CiteDrive s aplikac\xed Overleaf\\n\\nPokud je\u0161t\u011b nejste p\u0159ihl\xe1\u0161eni do [Overleaf](https://www.overleaf.com/), mus\xedte tak u\u010dinit nyn\xed. Pot\xe9 p\u0159ejd\u011bte do [CiteDrive](https://www.citedrive.com/), vytvo\u0159te projekt Overleaf a do nov\xe9ho projektu [p\u0159idejte reference](https://citedrive.medium.com/adding-bibliographic-references-to-overleaf-with-citedrive-325f131e3ca2). V\xe1\u0161 projekt m\u016f\u017ee vypadat takto:\\n\\n![CiteDrive - P\u0159\xedklad](@site/static/img/tutorial/citedrive_project_example.png).\\n\\nPot\xe9 klikn\u011bte na \\"bib\\" v lev\xe9m horn\xedm rohu va\u0161eho projektu. T\xedm se otev\u0159e nov\xe1 karta dynamick\xe9ho souboru BibTeX, kter\xfd m\u016f\u017eete pou\u017e\xedt pro sv\u016fj Overleaf a kter\xfd se bude automaticky aktualizovat, kdykoli vy nebo va\u0161i kolegov\xe9 z t\xfdmu p\u0159id\xe1te, aktualizujete nebo odstran\xedte odkazy ve va\u0161em projektu.\\n\\n\\n\\nNakonec p\u0159ejd\u011bte do aplikace Overleaf, vytvo\u0159te nov\xfd soubor, vyberte mo\u017enost \\"Z extern\xed adresy URL\\" a vlo\u017ete adresu URL z dynamick\xe9ho BibTeXu do polo\u017eky \\"URL pro na\u010dten\xed souboru\\" a pojmenujte ji zde *references.bib*.\\nV\xe1\u0161 projekt CiteDrive je nyn\xed p\u0159ipojen k Overleafu! Nezapome\u0148te, \u017ee p\u0159i zm\u011bn\xe1ch v na\u0161em projektu CiteDrive mus\xedte kliknout na obnovit, aby Overleaf z\xedskal nejnov\u011bj\u0161\xed stav.\\n\\n![P\u0159idat soubory do Overleaf](@site/static/img/tutorial/export_bib_to_overleaf.png)\\n\\n## Krok 2: Vytvo\u0159en\xed dokumentu TeX v aplikaci Overleaf\\n\\nNyn\xed vytvo\u0159\xedme nov\xfd texov\xfd soubor pro Overleaf, kter\xfd m\u016f\u017eeme nazvat \\"document.tex\\", m\u016f\u017eeme definovat bibliografii, soubor BibTeX z CiteDrive pomoc\xed `\\\\bibliography{references}`. Jak\xe9 bibliografick\xe9 n\xe1stroje bychom v\u0161ak m\u011bli pou\u017e\xedt? Pro spr\xe1vu bibliografie v LaTeXu/Overleafu existuje mnoho mo\u017enost\xed: s nejv\u011bt\u0161\xed pravd\u011bpodobnost\xed natbib, bibtex a biblatex. Pro spr\xe1vu bibliografi\xed v LaTeXu je z\xe1kladem BibTeX, kter\xfd tvo\u0159\xed z\xe1klad form\xe1tu. Pomoc\xed natbib je BibTeX vybaven roz\u0161\xed\u0159en\xedm, kter\xe9 nab\xedz\xed v\u011bt\u0161\xed volnost p\u0159i n\xe1vrhu citac\xed v textu, a biblatex je kompletn\xed reviz\xed BibTeXu, kter\xe1 nab\xedz\xed v\xedce typ\u016f odkaz\u016f, mo\u017enost\xed t\u0159\xedd\u011bn\xed a filtrov\xe1n\xed bibliografi\xed a mo\u017enost\xed lokalizace. A\u010dkoli je BibteX nejzn\xe1m\u011bj\u0161\xedm programem, BibLaTex je nejen stejn\u011b robustn\xed, ale tak\xe9 nejv\xedce doporu\u010dovan\xfd program pro nov\xe1\u010dky. Cita\u010dn\xed a bibliografick\xe9 \xfadaje pro odkazy a seznamy jsou uchov\xe1v\xe1ny v tzv. souboru .bib, stejn\u011b jako je tomu v souboru BibTeX z CiteDrive. Je v\u017edy ve stejn\xe9m form\xe1tu:\\n\\n ```latex\\n @article{smith201X,\\n \\ttitle        = {An interesting article},\\n \\tauthor       = {John Smith},\\n \\tyear         = {201X},\\n \\tjournal      = {Journal of Interesting Articles}\\n }\\n ```\\n\\n Zde `@article` je typ zdroje, `title`, `author`, `year` a `journal` jsou atributy pou\u017e\xedvan\xe9 pro zobrazen\xed v seznamech odkaz\u016f a citac\xed a nakonec `smith201X` je jedine\u010dn\xfd identifik\xe1tor, kter\xfd m\u016f\u017eete pou\u017e\xedt pro odkazov\xe1n\xed v dokumentu, p\u0159edev\u0161\xedm pomoc\xed cite(key). CiteDrive nen\xed vyb\xedrav\xfd, pokud jde o form\xe1t; p\u0159ijateln\xe9 je jak\xe9koli pole a typ z\xe1znamu, kter\xfd umo\u017e\u0148uje pr\xe1ci s bibliografick\xfdm bal\xedkem podle va\u0161eho v\xfdb\u011bru. Proto\u017ee z\xe1kladn\xedm c\xedlem CiteDrive je odd\u011blit bibliografick\xe9 \xfadaje od dokumentu a cita\u010dn\xedch styl\u016f, podporuje CiteDrive v\u0161echny alternativy.\\n\\n\\n N\xed\u017ee proto uv\xe1d\xedme t\u0159i \u0161ablony, kter\xe9 v\xe1m pomohou za\u010d\xedt.\\n\\n ### Za\u010d\xedn\xe1me s BibTeXem:\\n\\n Pokud chcete za\u010d\xedt s BibTeXem, pou\u017eijte n\xe1sleduj\xedc\xed \u0161ablonu nebo ji otev\u0159ete p\u0159\xedmo v Overleafu. Dal\u0161\xed informace o BibTeXu naleznete v dokumentaci.\\n\\n ```latex title=\\"document.tex\\"\\n \\\\documentclass{article}\\n \\\\usepackage[utf8]{inputenc}\\n\\n \\\\title{BibTeX references in \\\\LaTeX}\\n \\\\author{John Smith}\\n\\n \\\\begin{document}\\n\\n \\\\maketitle\\n\\n Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Praesent enim urna, dapibus et bibendum vel, consectetur et turpis. Cras a molestie nulla. \\\\cite{Hemingway1952}\\n \\\\medskip\\n\\n \\\\bibliographystyle{unsrt}\\n \\\\bibliography{references}\\n\\n \\\\end{document}\\n ```\\n\\n\\n ### Za\u010d\xedn\xe1me s natbib:\\n\\n ```latex\\n \\\\documentclass{article}\\n \\\\usepackage{natbib}\\n \\\\bibliographystyle{apalike}\\n \\\\title{A Short Guide to Reference Management using natbib with BibTeX}\\n \\\\author{CiteDrive}\\n \\\\date {January 1988}\\n\\n \\\\begin{document}\\n\\n \\\\maketitle\\n \\\\textbf{Narrative citation:} \\\\citet{Doe:1966} investigated the risks of incorrectly \\\\\\\\\\n recorded [...], which results in distortion.\\n \\\\textbf{Parenthetical citation:} The risks of incorrect recording of [...] could lead to distortion\\n \\\\citep{Doe:1966}.\\n\\n \\\\medskip\\n\\n \\\\bibliography{references}\\n\\n \\\\end{document}\\n\\n ```\\n\\n\\n V\xedce informac\xed o natbib naleznete zde.\\n\\n ### Za\u010d\xedn\xe1me s BibLaTeXem.\\n\\n ```latex\\n \\\\documentclass{article}\\n \\\\usepackage{biblatex}\\n \\\\addbibresource{references.bib}\\n\\n \\\\begin{document}\\n Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Praesent enim urna, dapibus et bibendum vel, consectetur et turpis. Cras a molestie nulla. \\\\cite{Hemingway1952}\\n \\\\medskip\\n\\n \\\\printbibliography\\n\\n \\\\end{document}\\n ```\\n\\n\\n\\n Dal\u0161\xed informace o BibLaTeXu naleznete zde.\\n\\n\\n\\n ## Krok 3: Citace v textu\\n\\n\\n\\n Pokud m\xe1te nainstalov\xe1no roz\u0161\xed\u0159en\xed prohl\xed\u017ee\u010de, m\u016f\u017eete vytv\xe1\u0159et citace tak, \u017ee vyberete text a kliknete na ikonu CiteDrive na panelu n\xe1stroj\u016f.\\n\\n\\n\\n Odkazy m\u016f\u017eete citovat tak\xe9 ru\u010dn\u011b pomoc\xed p\u0159\xedkazu cite. Pokud byste nap\u0159\xedklad cht\u011bli citovat Smitha (201X), pou\u017eili byste p\u0159\xedkaz `\\\\cite{smith201X}`. Nebo pou\u017eijte vyhled\xe1v\xe1n\xed odkaz\u016f v overleafu.\\n\\n\\n\\n Bibliografick\xe9 styly jsou v Overleafu p\u0159edinstalov\xe1ny a podle toho, kter\xfd bal\xedk jste pou\u017eili, jsou odkazy na n\xe1sleduj\xedc\xedch str\xe1nk\xe1ch:\\n\\n\\n\\n To je v\u0161e! Nyn\xed byste m\u011bli m\xedt v\u0161e, co pot\u0159ebujete, abyste mohli za\u010d\xedt pou\u017e\xedvat reference v aplikaci Overleaf. Pokud m\xe1te n\u011bjak\xe9 dotazy nebo p\u0159ipom\xednky, dejte n\xe1m v\u011bd\u011bt e-mailem na adresu hello@citedrive.com.\\n\\n\\n\\n \u0160\u0165astn\xe9 a vesel\xe9 TeXov\xe1n\xed!"},{"id":"how-to-convert-a-doi-to-a-bibtex-citation-using-citedrive","metadata":{"permalink":"/cs/blog/how-to-convert-a-doi-to-a-bibtex-citation-using-citedrive","editUrl":"https://github.com/citedrive/bibtex.eu/blog/blog/2022-08-12-overleaf-cite.md","source":"@site/i18n/cs/docusaurus-plugin-content-blog/2022-08-12-overleaf-cite.md","title":"Jak p\u0159ev\xe9st DOI na citaci v BibTeXu pomoc\xed CiteDrive","description":"Pokud se zab\xfdv\xe1te v\xfdzkumem, pak v\xedte, jak d\u016fle\u017eit\xe9 jsou bibliografie a citace. A pokud pou\u017e\xedv\xe1te CiteDrive, pak v\xedte, \u017ee je to nejjednodu\u0161\u0161\xed zp\u016fsob, jak vytv\xe1\u0159et bibliografie a citace pro va\u0161e v\xfdzkumn\xe9 pr\xe1ce. Co ale d\u011blat, kdy\u017e m\xedsto ISBN nebo URL naraz\xedte na DOI? Nebojte se - m\xe1me pro v\xe1s \u0159e\u0161en\xed! V tomto p\u0159\xedsp\u011bvku na blogu v\xe1m uk\xe1\u017eeme, jak p\u0159ev\xe9st DOI na citaci v BibTeXu pomoc\xed aplikace CiteDrive. Za\u010dn\u011bme!","date":"2022-08-12T00:00:00.000Z","formattedDate":"12. srpna 2022","tags":[{"label":"citedrive","permalink":"/cs/blog/tags/citedrive"},{"label":"bibtex","permalink":"/cs/blog/tags/bibtex"},{"label":"doi","permalink":"/cs/blog/tags/doi"}],"readingTime":1.345,"hasTruncateMarker":false,"authors":[{"name":"CiteDrive","title":"https://www.CiteDrive.com/","mail":"hello@citedrive.com","url":"https://www.CiteDrive.com/","image_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/65911387?s=200&v=4","imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/65911387?s=200&v=4"}],"frontMatter":{"slug":"how-to-convert-a-doi-to-a-bibtex-citation-using-citedrive","title":"Jak p\u0159ev\xe9st DOI na citaci v BibTeXu pomoc\xed CiteDrive","authors":{"name":"CiteDrive","title":"https://www.CiteDrive.com/","mail":"hello@citedrive.com","url":"https://www.CiteDrive.com/","image_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/65911387?s=200&v=4","imageURL":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/65911387?s=200&v=4"},"tags":["citedrive","bibtex","doi"]},"prevItem":{"title":"Citov\xe1n\xed a pou\u017e\xedv\xe1n\xed odkaz\u016f na Overleafu: P\u0159\xedru\u010dka pro v\xfdzkumn\xe9 pracovn\xedky","permalink":"/cs/blog/citing-and-using-references-on-overleaf-a-guide-for-researchers"}},"content":"Pokud se zab\xfdv\xe1te v\xfdzkumem, pak v\xedte, jak d\u016fle\u017eit\xe9 jsou bibliografie a citace. A pokud pou\u017e\xedv\xe1te [CiteDrive](https://www.citedrive.com/), pak v\xedte, \u017ee je to nejjednodu\u0161\u0161\xed zp\u016fsob, jak vytv\xe1\u0159et bibliografie a citace pro va\u0161e v\xfdzkumn\xe9 pr\xe1ce. Co ale d\u011blat, kdy\u017e m\xedsto ISBN nebo URL naraz\xedte na [DOI](/fields/doi/)? Nebojte se - m\xe1me pro v\xe1s \u0159e\u0161en\xed! V tomto p\u0159\xedsp\u011bvku na blogu v\xe1m uk\xe1\u017eeme, jak p\u0159ev\xe9st DOI na citaci v BibTeXu pomoc\xed aplikace CiteDrive. Za\u010dn\u011bme!\\n\\n\\n\\n## Pou\u017eit\xed roz\u0161\xed\u0159en\xed prohl\xed\u017ee\u010de\\nP\u0159evod DOI na citaci v BibTeXu je snadn\xfd, pokud pou\u017e\xedv\xe1te roz\u0161\xed\u0159en\xed prohl\xed\u017ee\u010de \'CiteDrive Companion\'. Sta\u010d\xed ozna\u010dit DOI my\u0161\xed, prav\xfdm tla\u010d\xedtkem my\u0161i otev\u0159\xedt kontextovou nab\xeddku a vybrat \'Search doi\'.\\n\\n![CiteDrive - P\u0159\xedklad](@site/static/img/tutorial/browserextension-search-doi.png)\\n\\nPot\xe9 se zobraz\xed n\xe1hled z\xe1znamu BibTeX, kde jej m\u016f\u017eete p\u0159ed ulo\u017een\xedm do vybran\xe9ho projektu zm\u011bnit.\\n\\n![CiteDrive - P\u0159\xedklad](@site/static/img/tutorial/browserextension-bibtex-preview.png)\\n\\n\\n\\n A je to! Spole\u010dn\xedka najdete v n\xe1sleduj\xedc\xedch prohl\xed\u017ee\u010d\xedch:\\n\\n* [CiteDrive Companion Plugin pro Google Chrome](https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/citedrive-bibtex-companio/gmmonfphegngpcbcapfbgembkjeookik)\\n* [CiteDrive Companion Plugin pro Mozilla Firefox](https://addons.mozilla.org/af/firefox/addon/citedrive-companion/)\\n* [CiteDrive Companion Plugin pro Microsoft Edge](https://microsoftedge.microsoft.com/addons/detail/citedrive-bibtex-compan/kpmepfpbjehnlgfbcnbmgihklkkmfnpo)\\n\\n\\n## Pomoc\xed online n\xe1stroje:\\nPokud roz\u0161\xed\u0159en\xed prohl\xed\u017ee\u010de nepou\u017e\xedv\xe1te, nezoufejte - i tak m\u016f\u017eete pou\u017e\xedt CiteDrive a p\u0159ev\xe9st DOI na citaci v BibTeXu. Sta\u010d\xed p\u0159ej\xedt na webov\xe9 str\xe1nky CiteDrive a vlo\u017eit sv\u016fj DOI do pole \\"Enter DOI\\", kter\xe9 najdete v \u010d\xe1sti Search via Doi po vyvol\xe1n\xed symbolu plus v horn\xed naviga\u010dn\xed li\u0161t\u011b. . Pak klikn\u011bte na tla\u010d\xedtko \'Convert\' a voil\xe1! - va\u0161e citace v BibTeXu se vygeneruje automaticky.\\n\\n![CiteDrive - P\u0159\xedklad](@site/static/img/tutorial/citedrive-search-doi.png)\\n\\n\\nDouf\xe1me, \u017ee v\xe1m tento p\u0159\xedsp\u011bvek pomohl. Pokud m\xe1te jak\xe9koli dotazy, nev\xe1hejte n\xe1s kontaktovat. V\u017edy v\xe1m r\xe1di pom\u016f\u017eeme!\\n\\nCiteDrive je nejjednodu\u0161\u0161\xed zp\u016fsob vytv\xe1\u0159en\xed bibliografi\xed a citac\xed pro va\u0161e v\u011bdeck\xe9 pr\xe1ce. P\u0159eve\u010fte DOI na citaci v BibTeXu pomoc\xed CiteDrive je\u0161t\u011b dnes! Vyzkou\u0161ejte si ji zdarma na str\xe1nk\xe1ch CiteDrive.com.\\n\\n\u0160\u0165astn\xe9 citov\xe1n\xed! :)"}]}')}}]);